<article style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;margin:0px;background-color:#F6F6F6;line-height: 1.5rem;font-style: italic;">
  <img style="width: 100%;" src="https://reapit-s3-policy-test.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/public/image-20191122-114228.png" />
  <h1 style="text-align: center; font-size: 34px; font-style: normal;">Forgot Password</h1>
  <div style="padding:0 20px 20px 50px;">
    <p>Hi <%= userName %>,</p>
    <br />
    <p>We have received a request to reset your Reapit Foundations password.</p>
    <p>Please click the button below to continue.</p>
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a style="border: solid thin #0061a8;padding: 10px;background-color: #0061a8;color: white;z-index: 1;text-decoration: none; font-style: normal;" href=<%= `${url}?userName=${userName}&verificationCode={####}` %>>RESET PASSWORD</a>
    </div>
    <p>If you did not make this request, please ignore this email.</p>
    <br />
    <p>Best Regards,</p>
    <p>Reapit Team</p>
  </div>
</article>
